headline: Williams Companies (NYSE:WMB) Completes Expansion Of Key Energy Projects Along Gulf Coast
summary: Williams Companies (NYSE:WMB) achieved an 11.92% increase in its share price over the last quarter, coinciding with the successful commissioning of key energy projects, the Southeast Energy Connector and Texas to Louisiana Energy Pathway. These expansions mark significant strides in meeting rising natural gas demand and transitioning toward cleaner energy.
